lead_paragraph: Barcelona leapfrogged Atletico Madrid to go top of La Liga after Lionel Messi's acrobatic volley secured a hard-fought 2-1 victory against tenacious Malaga on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Barca Back on Top After Messi Stunner
